title: Did you show up in the news report months ago?
subtitle: An activist in the right-wing social media saw evidence of a conspiracy where there was nothing in the pictures of Margaret Keenan of December 2020.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: Margaret Keenan, the first recipient of the Vizer/BUTCH COVID-19 vaccine in December 2020, was presented in a news report two months ago, providing evidence of errors or deception.
